set="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Olivia-Rodrigo-Jack-White-and-St.-Vincent.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Olivia-Rodrigo-Jack-White-and-St.-Vincent-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Olivia-Rodrigo-Jack-White-and-St.-Vincent-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Olivia-Rodrigo-Jack-White-and-St.-Vincent-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Olivia-Rodrigo-Jack-White-and-St.-Vincent-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Olivia-Rodrigo-Jack-White-and-St.-Vincent-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/olivia-rodrigo">奥利维亚·罗德里戈</a>分享了<a href="/artists/jack-white">杰克·怀特</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/st-vincent">圣文森特</a>在创作她的专辑“Guts”时给她的建议。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/olivia-rodrigo-cover-interview-2021-sour-drivers-license-2940697"><em>NME</em>大读物 – 奥利维亚·罗德里戈 (Olivia Rodrigo)：“作为一名歌曲作者，受到认真对待对我来说很重要”</a></strong></li></ul><p>在最近接受<a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/08/24/arts/music/olivia-rodrigo-guts.html?smid=nytcore-ios-share&amp;referringSource=articleShare" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《纽约时报》</em></a>采访时，罗德里戈解释了她如何在创作新专辑的压力下向怀特寻求帮助。</p><p> “我第一次见到他时，他给我写了这封信，信中写道，‘你唯一的工作就是创作你想在广播中听到的音乐，’”她说。这位歌手接着补充道：“我的意思是，写出你想在广播中听到的歌曲实际上非常困难。”</p><p>圣文森特是罗德里戈在创作专辑期间与之交谈的另一位音乐家，并将他视为导师。圣文森特（真名安妮·克拉克）在接受<a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/08/24/arts/music/olivia-rodrigo-guts.html?smid=nytcore-ios-share&amp;referringSource=articleShare" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《纽约时报》</em></a>电话采访时表示：“我从未见过如此年轻、如此泰然自若的人。 [罗德里戈]知道她是谁，她想要什么——而且似乎一点也不害怕表达出来。而且也是一个非常可爱的女孩，”她补充道。 “我从来没有听她说过任何人的坏话。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/Cv9PQWNrkzS/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" 